             was indicted for <rs id="t17890909-16-off82" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17890909-16-off82" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-16-off82" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17890909-16-cd83" type="crimeDate">5th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-16-off82 t17890909-16-cd83"></join> last, a watch in a gold case, value 5 l. another watch with a metal outside covered with shagreen, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17890909-16-victim178" type="victimName">
